</P>
<P>
 Lake Casitas will be the site of the third annual Ojai Renaissance Festival, 
featuring medieval costumes, stage performances, jousting tournaments, arts, 
crafts, food, parades and more. Hours: 10 a.m. to dusk each day. $6 adults, $5 
students, $4 seniors and children 12 and younger, age 3 and younger free. 
Information: 646-8126. 
</P>
<P>
