 The Alzheimer's Assn. of Ventura County will hold "Walk With Me," the 24th 
annual Alzheimer's Assn. Memory Walk, a 4-mile walk-a-thon along the coast 
starting at 9 a.m. at San Buenaventura State Beach; registration at 8 a.m. 
Funds to benefit the association's support and education services. Information: 
643-2614. 
</P>
<P>
