</P>
<P>
 Juggler and storyteller Izzy Tooinsky will open the Ventura County Children's 
Festival, 1994-95 family concert series at the new Thousand Oaks Civic Arts 
Plaza, Forum Theater. $7 children, $9 adults; season tickets $55 children, $65 
adults. Advance tickets and information 646-6997. 
</P>
<P>
