</P>
<P>
 The Pleasant Valley Recreation and Park District will present the Fall Arts & 
Crafts Fair from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. at the Camarillo Community Center, Burnley 
St. Singers, dancers, clowns, handmade crafts, paintings, ceramics, jewelry and 
more. Free admission. Information: 482-1996. 
</P>
