 The Eleventh Hour Breast Cancer Awareness Walk, Rally & Fair will be held at 
Bennett Park, Westlake Village and the Esplanade Mall, Oxnard. Co-sponsored by 
the American Cancer Society, Futurecare Cancer Treatment Center-Oxnard and the 
Westlake Comprehensive Cancer Center. Information: 983-8864. 
</P>
<P>
