<P>
WHAT'S THE DEAL: BODY WATCH; CLEAN WATER FOR HAPPY CAMPERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Campers in remote areas are wise to be skeptical of the water supply.Some 
options and costs of playing it safe: 
</P>
<P>
 * Diet Coke, six-pack, $1.89. 
</P>
<P>
 * Potable Aqua purification tablets, 50 for about $3.95. 
</P>
<P>
 * Corona Extra beer, six-pack, $5.99. 
</P>
<P>
 * PUR Scout filter, $60 and up. KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
