<P>
DI-TECH SOLD TO FLORIDA COMPANY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Florida company said Monday it has agreed to purchase Di-Tech Inc.'s assets 
and operations. 
</P>
<P>
 Based in Brea, Di-Tech manufactures water purification systems and has annual 
revenue of more than $1 million. It is a division of privately held Coast 
Filter Media Supply Co. 
</P>
